WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.560
This technological shift creates tension between business outcomes and human

00:00:04.560 --> 00:00:09.120
outcomes. Stagility is the balance between creating stability for workers

00:00:09.120 --> 00:00:13.680
while allowing the organization to move with extreme agility. Reflect

00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:18.240
on the practical payoff of this balance: providing stable anchors

00:00:18.240 --> 00:00:22.800
like core values allows people to feel safe enough to

00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:27.360
innovate rapidly. Radical employee centricity involves partnering with employees to

00:00:27.360 --> 00:00:31.920
eliminate low-value work. This requires Empathy. Cognitive empathy takes their

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:36.480
perspective, emotional empathy shares their feelings, and empathic concern senses

00:00:36.480 --> 00:00:41.040
what they need and takes decisive action.
